main event: A witness in Riverdale, New York reported seeing a bluish, hovering unidentified flying object on August 9, 1969 between 3:00 AM and 3:30 AM.
interesting points: The object appeared to have rings around it.
The object made a sharp turn and went out of sight after about 1 minute.
The witness could not identify the object and reported it to the Air Force for investigation.
The Air Force requested the witness complete an AF Form 117 to provide more details about the sighting.
The Air Force's Project Blue Book was tasked with investigating the sighting, though the available information was deemed insufficient.
sighted object: a bluish, hovering unidentified flying object
